## Name of the node
-${SHORT_NAME_PREFIX}name ${NODE_NAME}

## Cookie for distributed erlang
-setcookie ${COOKIE}

## Diagnostic for reltest CI hang: force init to halt the VM 30s after
## init:stop is called, so `antidote stop` can't block indefinitely on a
## slow application shutdown. Any app still alive after this deadline is
## killed, which means the logs will show exactly who failed to stop in time.
-shutdown_time 30000

## Enable time warp once Issue #226 is fixed
##+C multi_time_warp
